perform new translations with the same `source` and `target` language, use <doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swiftui/view/translationtask(_:action:)>"},{"text":"and call <doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/translation/translationsession/configuration/invalidate()>."},{"text":""},{"text":"For example, you can translate when content appears:"},{"text":""},{"text":"     struct ContentView: View {"},{"text":"         var sourceText = \"Hallo, Welt!\""},{"text":"         var sourceLanguage: Locale.Language?"},{"text":"         var targetLanguage: Locale.Language?"},{"text":""},{"text":"         @State private var targetText: String?"},{"text":""},{"text":"         var body: some View {"},{"text":"             Text(targetText ?? sourceText)"},{"text":"                 .translationTask("},{"text":"                     source: sourceLanguage,"},{"text":"                     target: targetLanguage"},{"text":"                 ) { session in"},{"text":"                     Task { @MainActor in"},{"text":"                         do {"},{"text":"                             let response = try await session.translate(sourceText)"},{"text":"                             targetText = response.targetText"},{"text":"                         } catch {"},{"text":"                             // Handle any errors."},{"text":"                         }"},{"text":"                     }"},{"text":"                 }"},{"text":"         }"},{"text":"     }"},{"text":""},{"text":"The system throws a `fatalError` if you use a <doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/translation/translationsession> instance after the attached view disappears or if you use it after"},{"text":"changing the `source` or `target` parameters. This causes the `action` closure to provide a new instance."},{"text":""},{"text":"- Parameters:"},{"text":"    - source: The language the source content is in. If this is `nil`, the session tries to"},{"text":"        identify the language and prompts the person to pick the source language if it's unclear. All"},{"text":"        text translated within the session should be in the same source language. Changing this"},{"text":"        value cancels previous tasks and creates a new session to perform translations again."},{"text":"    - target: The language to translate content into. A `nil` value means the session picks a"},{"text":"        target according to the person's `Locale.preferredLanguages` and the `source`."},{"text":"        Changing this value cancels previous tasks and creates a new one to perform"},{"text":"        translations again."},{"text":"    - action: A closure that runs when the view first appears and when `source` or"},{"text":"        `target` change.  It provides a <doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/translation/translationsession> instance to perform"},{"text":"        one or multiple translations."}]},"functionSignature":{"parameters":[{"name":"source","declarationFragments":[{"kind":"identifier","spelling":"source"},{"kind":"text","spelling":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","spelling":"Locale","preciseIdentifier":"s:10Foundation6LocaleV"},{"kind":"text","spelling":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","spelling":"Language","preciseIdentifier":"s:10Foundation6LocaleV8LanguageV"},{"kind":"text","spelling":"?"}]},{"name":"target","declarationFragments":[{"kind":"identifier","spelling":"target"},{"kind":"text","spelling":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","spelling":"Locale","preciseIdentifier":"s:10Foundation6LocaleV"},{"kind":"text","spelling":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","spelling":"Language","preciseIdentifier":"s:10Foundation6LocaleV8LanguageV"},{"kind":"text","spelling":"?"}]},{"name":"action","declarationFragments":[{"kind":"identifier","spelling":"action"},{"kind":"text","spelling":": ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","spelling":"TranslationSession","preciseIdentifier":"s:11Translation0A7SessionC"},{"kind":"text","spelling":") "},{"kind":"keyword","spelling":"async"},{"kind":"text","spelli